[ &lt;a href=&quot;https://svn.apache.org/r1756835&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://svn.apache.org/r1756835&lt;/a&gt; ]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PDFBOX-3467&quot; title=&quot;PDPage.getAnnotations() modifies the PDF&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PDFBOX-3467&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PDFBOX-3467&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;: don&apos;t modify during getAnnotations&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15426819" author="jahewson" created="Thu, 18 Aug 2016 17:05:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ok, sorted!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
